thing that gets me too is, both clerics I had to ask for buffs repeatedly.  One cleric told me that he didnt want to "waste" a symbol on me.  WASTE??  hmm, I thought the idea was to buff the MA up as much as possible.  I even carry peridots and jaspers on me in case that is the problem.  But why would a cleric see it as a waste to symbol the main tank?<br><br>I dont know where they are coming from but there are some VERY SHITTY clerics out there these days.  I know there are many decent clerics and a few great ones out there as well.  I wondered briefly if they were ebays but I dont think they were.  They were just shitty clerics, that let their tank die, even though they were not out of mana or were not getting hit on.  Neither one saw it fit to apologize to me either, so I did not bother to thank them for the rez.<br><br>I am going to be VERY careful about who I group with from now on.  I started out with less than a blue to ding 51 and ended up  over 2 blues away from 51.  Thats not the direction I wanna go!!  PLEASE tell me it was NOT a common thing and that they really did just make an honest mistake and that it wont happen ever again!!  <br><br>Smacker 50war<br>Milo 60dru <p><p><img src=http://www.kerinakreation.com/images/sigs/blewssig.jpg WIDTH=500 HEIGHT=250 border=0></p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#D5D4D5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ustanbuhrs.showPublicProfile?language=EN>stanbuhrs</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>h0x0r!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(1/15/02 9:34:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumwarrior.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=471.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.kc.rr.com/istrahd/mountainking-dither.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Fuggin Clerics</span><hr size=1> Heh hey milo!!! I think there are more good clerics than bad.. i cant remember the las